room_title: Escape room "Foreign Agent" by Premier Escape Rooms in San Antonio
room_address: 19186 Blanco Rd Ste 102 San Antonio, TX 78258
room_description: You've entered the room of an intelligence official to find a classified document that will prove he is committing espionage and selling secrets to an enemy country. After your team enters the office the door closes behind you and locks. Now you must find the classified document and the diamonds that he is being paid for the information. Then figure out how to get out before he gets back from his one-hour lunch appointment. Who knows what he will do to you if he finds you in his office...
